title: Catfish: Trolls
overview: Radio host, television star and internet provocateur Charlamagne Tha God, and co-host Raymond Braun, will give everything they've got to stop internet trolls, the most pervasive and consistent troublemakers online. Using the "Catfish" brand of investigating the truth, Catfish: Trolls unmasks the internet's most vocal trolls to drag them out of hiding and into the light.
